  Lang5 tiam3 se3-kan te7-it ai3--e5, chiu7-si7 peng5-an, khoai3-lok8, ho2-giah8, iong2-kiaN7, tng5 hoe3-siu7, kiaN2-sun che7, te7-ui7 koan5. Chiu7-si7 ai3 tit moa2-i3 e5 jin5-seng. Ia7 te7-it m7-ai3--e5, chiu7-si7 chhiN-chham2, kan-khou2, san3-hiong, soe-lam2, iau2-chiat, kou-toaN, pi-bi5. Chiu7-si7 m7-ai3 put-ju5-i3 e5 seng-oah8. 
  Ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, lan2 chiu7 eng7 chin7 sou2-u7 e5 ti3-hui7 kap khui3-lat8, lai5 tui-kiu5 te7-it ho2 e5 jin5-seng, ia7 chin7-liong7 ai3 pi7-bian2 it-chhe3 te7-it m7-ho2 e5 seng-oah8. 
  TaN na7 lang5-lang5 sou2 teh tui-kiu5--e5, long2 tat8-chiaN5, chiu7 se3-kan si7 bo5 sim2-mih8 kan-khou2, a2-si7 khun3-lan5. Chong2-si7 su7-sit8 po3 lan2 chai “Jin5-seng” peng7 m7-si7 chiah-nih kan2-tan, in-ui7 chit8-bin7 ko2-jian5 se3-kan u7 che7-che7 lang5 tit-tioh8 moa2-i3 e5 jin5-seng, siang5-si5 koh chit8 bin7 ia7 si7 u7 che7-che7 lang5 teh keng-koe3 put-ju5-i3 e5 seng-oah8. Chiu7 siang5 chit8 e5 lang5 ia7 e7 keng-giam7-tioh8 chit nng7-cheng2 e5 keng2-gu7, chhin-chhiuN7 chau2-be2-teng, lai5 koh khi3, khi3 koh lai5, bo5 theng5-hioh. 
  Siat-su2 jin5-seng na7 chi2 han7-tiaN7 ti7 chit but8-chit e5 se3-kan, chiu7-si7 kau3 si2 chiu7 soah lah! Ki5-sit8 m7-si7 an2-ni, in-ui7 sim2-mih8 lang5 to chin chheng-chho2, ia7 chin beng5-pek8, tu5-khi3 but8-chit e7 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 seng-oah8 i2-goa7, iau2 u7 chit8 e5 boe7 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 “Leng5-seng3” seng-oah8. Lan2 thang tui3 jin5-lui7 sou2-u7 it-chhe3 e5 chong-kau3 seng-oah8 lai5 tit-tioh8 cheng3-beng5. 
  TaN chit e5 leng5-seng3 e5 seng-oah8 sou2 teh tui-kiu5--e5, goan5-chek-siong7 iu5-goan5 kap but8-chit seng-oah8 e5 tui-kiu5 siang5-khoan2, long2 si7 ai3 ho2 m7-ai3 phaiN2. Ia7 hit e5 ho2 e5 hong-bin7, chiu7-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 lang5 ai3 se3-kan ho2 e5 seng-oah8 an2-ni, ai3 tit-tioh8 ti7 “ThiN”--nih u7 ho2 e5 seng-oah8 e5 sou2-chai7, chiu7-si7 it-poaN kio3-cho3 “Thian-tong5” e5. Ia7 sou2 m7-ai3 e5 phaiN2 e5 hong-bin7, si7 pi2 m7-ai3 se3-kan phaiN2 e5 seng-oah8, koh-khah m7-ai3. In-ui7 se3-kan phaiN2 e5 seng-oah8, kau3 si2 chiu7 oan5-kiat, koh m7-si7 kau3 hiah li7-hai7; na7-si7 leng5-seng3 phaiN2 e5 seng-oah8, chiu7-si7 kau3-kek8 e5 chhiN-chham2 kap khou2-thang3, hit e5 sou2-chai7 kio3-cho3 “Te7-gek8.” 
  Te7-bin7-chiuN7 but8-chit e5 seng-oah8, siong5-siong5 e7-thang tui3 lang5 e5 leng5-lek8 lai5 khek-hok8, a2-si7 pian3-oaN7, hou7 sou2 m7-ai3 e5 phaiN2 e5 jin5-seng, pian3-cho3 ho2 e5 jin5-seng; ia7 hou7 phaiN2 seng-oah8 e5 tiuN5-sou2, pian3-oaN7 cho3 ho2 seng-oah8 e5 tiuN5-sou2. Chong2-si7 leng5-seng3 e5 seng-oah8 chiu7 be7-thang an2-ni e5 chu7-iu5. “Thian-tong5 te7-gek8” si7 siok8 ti7 bu5-heng5 e5 se3-kai3, m7-si7 lang5 e7-thang chu7-iu5 soan2-tek8. Sou2-i2 tui3 ti7 te7-gek8 e5 ui-hiap8 (kiaN-ui3), si7 hui-siong5 e5 giam5-tiong7. Ui7-tioh8 kiaN-liau2 tioh8 loh8 te7-gek8, chiu7 koh-khah ai3 kau3 thian-tong5. 
