  Ia7 li2 siuN7 te7-gek8 si7 sim2-mih8 khoan2 e5 sou2-chai7? Si7 teh siu-iong5 kap jiok8-the2 pun-li7 e5 “leng5-hun5,” keng-koe3 chit8 toaN7 e5 ki5-kan siu7 heng5-hoat8. Moa2-ki5 liau2-au7, tit-tioh8 lun5-hoe5 choan2-seng, chiu7 thang tui3 hia chhut--lai5 mah? Li2 na7 an2-ni siuN7, chiu7 toa7 chho3-gou7. ChhiaN2 li2 iu5-goan5 thiaN Seng3-keng e5 oe7, chiu7 e7 hou7 li2 tit-tioh8 chheng-chho2, beng5-pek8, koat-toan3 piau2-hian7 li2 sou2 tioh8 chhu2 e5 thai3-tou7. 
  Seng3-keng Lou7-ka 16:19-31 sou2 ki3 e5, put-ko3 si7 hou7 lang5 sio2-khoa2 thang chai te7-gek8 e5 cheng5-heng5. Chong2-si7 na7 thak8 Ma2-thai3 25:41, chiu7 hou7 lan2 koh-khah thang beng5-pek8 te7-gek8 e5 choat8-bang7. Chiu7-si7 “Siu7 chiu3-chou2 e5,” tioh8 “Jip8 eng2-oan2 e5 hoe2, chiu7-si7 ui7-tioh8 Mou5-kui2......sou2 pi7-pan7 e5.” 
  Li2 ai3 kau3 “Thian-tong5,” pi7-bian2 kau3 “Te7-gek8” mah? Tioh8 bat Siong7-te3, sin3 Siong7-te3, thiaN Siong7-te3 e5 ka3-si7, chun-siu2 lai5 kiaN5, chiu7 e7 tit-tioh8. Chiu7-si7 tioh8 siong5-siong5 kau3 le2-pai3-tng5 thiaN to7-li2, kap siong5-siong5 ti3-i3 thak8 Seng3-keng, sit8-heng5 li2 sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 ka3-si7. 
